title: Nintendo Gamer April 2012
description:
Nintendo Gamer April 2012

Ngamer Magazine No other mag gives you so much Nintendo: new games 
picked apart in unseemly detail; the latest titles reviewed by the 
best writers in the business; dedicated Virtual Console and WiFi 
sections and a huge World of Nintendo section that brings you Zelda 
tattoos, Wii-playing hamsters, Wii Sports birthday cakes and 
Metroid piano concerto.

English | 132 pages | HQ PDF | 100.00 Mb
